    "Most of the students are international students.",
    "They did not grow up in America and they are not familiar with Americana (such as metaphors involving American baseball).",
    "Although web search also works well on metaphors and Americana, my students tended to prefer ChatGPT, perhaps because it is the new hot thing, or perhaps because bots are easier to use (and require fewer clicks than web search).",
    "I was surprised how well ChatGPT did on metaphors, but I was also surprised how poorly it did on references.",
    "If you ask ChatGPT for references on some topic, it will make up papers that do not stand up to fact-checking."
